data.description: Living on one level! This 1,400 sf home is located just one block N of the LM School. The exterior features a brand new fenced in backyard, brick accents in the front, and a detached one stall garage with large workshop attached to it that has a 2nd story loft! The home itself boasts a large kitchen w/newer cabinets and sit up island, tons of pantry storage and a built in desk. Dishwasher, microwave, stove, washer & dryer will stay. New laminate floor throughout the living room which has a bay window overlooking the street. There are three main level bedrooms and one full bath. The LL has been gutted and is ready for a facelift-studded out and new can lighting already complete. Give your favorite realtor a call today!
